We are creating a post request to submit an order. once the order id is created. we are getting the order information and order ID from get request. The response we are getting from the get request. we are checking that response whether the order id is as same order id or not when the order was created. so, for that we are adding one more validation point in the get request. Now to delete the request we don’t need the body but we are passing some validation of status code and also, we are deleting the all the environment ids.

Post -> Order ID-> Get ->Response
	Order ID->Delete

